data.description: Discover the epitome of coastal living in this exquisite 5-bedroom, 4 1/2-bathroom single-family home located in the heart of Orange Beach's coveted Terry Cove subdivision. From the moment you step onto the property, you're greeted by a perfect blend of elegance and comfort.This spacious residence offers a thoughtfully designed floor plan, seamlessly integrating both functionality and style. Step outside to your private oasis, where an inground pool awaits, promising countless moments of relaxation and entertainment. One of the standout features of this property is the private boat launch and boat storage, allowing you to seamlessly transition from your home to the water. This home is not just a residence; it's a gateway to the Orange Beach lifestyle. Seize the opportunity to make it yours. Schedule a showing today and envision the endless possibilities of coastal living.
